Pros and cons

According to our mobile phone expert
  • You can take sharp and detailed photos with the 3 rear cameras, even when you zoom in.
  • With the useful Camera Control button, you can zoom in, focus, and quickly take a photo.
  • Thanks to the fluent movements on the ProMotion display, your iPhone feels super fast.
  • This large iPhone doesn't fit in your pocket and is heavy in your hand.
  • If you download often and take a lot of photos, your storage space fills up in a few years.

Description

The Apple iPhone 16 Pro Max 256GB White Titanium has a large screen and a very good cameras. You can see every detail in movies and games on the bright 6.9-inch screen. Scrolling and gaming looks smooth and less choppy thanks to the high refresh rate. This makes your iPhone feel even faster. You can zoom up to 5 times without your photos becoming grainy with the telephoto lens. You can also take sharp photos from very up close or in the dark. With the new Camera Control button, you can control your camera easily. Slide over the button to zoom in, and press lightly to focus, for example. Thanks to this powerful chip, the most demanding apps and games run smoothly. If you download complete seasons and take a lot of photos and videos, you have to delete files in a few years. Choose the 512GB storage, so you don't have to do this.

Insure your mobile phone

You can choose one of the ERGO Insurance policies below in your shopping cart. The insurance can be canceled every year, with the right to a refund of the overpaid premium.
These insurances are governed by Belgian law. ERGO is a German insurer. If you have a complaint, you can contact the or our customer service .

Coverage

  • Fall and impact damage
  • Manufacturing errors outside the warranty
  • Water damage
  • Theft (Optional)

What isn't covered?

  • Damage caused by gross negligence isn't covered
  • Damage that doesn't affect the product functioning (such as dents) isn't covered

ERGO Mobile devices insurance excluding theft

  • Can be canceled monthly (179,88 per year) 14,99 per month
  • 1-year advance payment (159,90 per year) 159,90 one-time payment

ERGO Mobile devices insurance including theft

  • Can be canceled monthly (203,88 per year) 16,99 per month
  • 1-year advance payment (174,90 per year) 174,90 one-time payment

Deductible

In case of damage, a deductible of 10% (repair) or 20% (theft) applies
